OL,3,CToddler suffered 'campaign of
OL,4,Cviolence' before death, jury hears
OL,6,F*Warning - this article includes
OL,7,Fdistressing content
OL,9,FA toddler whose mother and her new
OL,10,Fboyfriend are accused of her murder
OL,11,Fand sexual assault suffered 21 broken
OL,12,Fbones in the weeks leading up to her
OL,13,Fdeath, a court heard.
OL,15,FIsabelle Welsh, two, collapsed at her
OL,16,Fhome in Hartington Close, Thornaby,
OL,17,FTeesside, having suffered a "massive
OL,18,Fhead injury", and could not be saved,
OL,19,Fjurors were told.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/11
