OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1782251281
OL,3,CToddler suffered 'campaign of
OL,4,Cviolence' before death, jury hears
OL,6,FHer mother, Alexandra Walker, 25, and
OL,7,FHarrison Simpson, 22, deny murder,
OL,8,Fallowing the death of a child, sexual
OL,9,Fassault and child cruelty and are on
OL,10,Ftrial at Teesside Crown Court.
OL,12,FThe couple had got together only last
OL,13,Fsummer and Simpson became a regular
OL,14,Fvisitor to Walker's home, spending "a
OL,15,Flot of time" with the little girl,
OL,16,Fjurors were told.
OL,26,@vD@dOUwD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/11
