PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1782251281
OL,3,CToddler suffered 'campaign of
OL,4,Cviolence' before death, jury hears
OL,6,FOn 13 September 2025, Walker made a
OL,7,F999 call about her daughter who had
OL,8,Fcollapsed, and paramedics found
OL,9,FIsabelle at the foot of the stairs,
OL,10,Fwithout a pulse and gravely ill.
OL,12,FRichard Wright KC, prosecuting, said
OL,13,Fshe was covered in bruises,
OL,14,Fparticularly to her head, neck,
OL,15,Fabdomen, back and private parts, her
OL,16,Fnappy contained blood and she had
OL,17,Fvomit on her face.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1782251281
OL,3,CToddler suffered 'campaign of
OL,4,Cviolence' before death, jury hears
OL,6,FShe was rushed to hospital by
OL,7,Fambulance, but despite the efforts of
OL,8,Fspecialist doctors, she died in the
OL,9,Fearly hours of 14 September.
OL,11,FThe prosecution said Isabelle had been
OL,12,Fviolently shaken, her spine over-
OL,13,Fextended, and her head hit against a
OL,14,Fhard surface such as a wall or the
OL,15,Ffloor.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1782251281
OL,3,CToddler suffered 'campaign of
OL,4,Cviolence' before death, jury hears
OL,6,FMr Wright said: "For weeks this child
OL,7,Fhad been violently assaulted and her
OL,8,Fdeath, by that terrible head injury,
OL,9,Fwas simply the end point in that
OL,10,Fcampaign of violence to which she had
OL,11,Fbeen subjected."
OL,13,FThe prosecution case was that both
OL,14,FWalker and Simpson had "ample
OL,15,Fopportunity" to harm the toddler and
OL,16,Fin such a small, two-bedroom house
OL,17,F"each must have been aware of the
OL,18,Fabuse".
OL,26,@yD@AOUzD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
