OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1782251281
OL,3,CToddler suffered 'campaign of
OL,4,Cviolence' before death, jury hears
OL,6,FMr Wright said Walker took her
OL,7,Fdaughter to the GP and then hospital
OL,8,F11 days before she died, when
OL,9,FIsabelle's leg was found to be
OL,10,Ffractured, and despite the concerns of
OL,11,Fsome medics, she was discharged back
OL,12,Finto her mother's care.
OL,14,FThe prosecution said this leg fracture
OL,15,Fwas "no more of an accident than the
OL,16,Ffatal head injury".
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
