OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1782251281
OL,3,CToddler suffered 'campaign of
OL,4,Cviolence' before death, jury hears
OL,6,FA post mortem examination found that
OL,7,FIsabelle had suffered fractures to 21
OL,8,Fbones and she was "covered in bruising
OL,9,Fthe result of forceful gripping", Mr
OL,10,FWright said.
OL,12,FThe prosecution said Walker, by her
OL,13,Fown account, had waited two weeks
OL,14,Fbefore reporting the fractured leg.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1782251281
OL,3,CToddler suffered 'campaign of
OL,4,Cviolence' before death, jury hears
OL,6,FMr Wright said: "When Isabelle was
OL,7,Fgravely unwell in the week before she
OL,8,Fdied no medical assistance was sought,
OL,9,Fand even on the day she died, after
OL,10,Fher heart had stopped and she appeared
OL,11,Fto all intents and purposes to be
OL,12,Fdead, Alexandra Walker only called an
OL,13,Fambulance when her stepfather told her
OL,14,Fto, long after she must have known her
OL,15,Fdaughter was critically ill.
OL,17,F"All of this, we will invite you to
OL,18,Fconclude, was not because of panic
OL,19,Fabout Isabelle, or a failure to
OL,20,Fappreciate how ill she was.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1782251281
OL,3,CToddler suffered 'campaign of
OL,4,Cviolence' before death, jury hears
OL,6,F"To the contrary, Alexandra Walker and
OL,7,FHarrison Simpson each plainly knew how
OL,8,Fill she was, they knew that because
OL,9,Fthey had caused her injuries and their
OL,10,Ffailure to summon help from doctors
OL,11,Fand finally the emergency services,
OL,12,Fwas an act of self-preservation.
OL,14,F"They knew the questions that would
OL,15,Fcome and had no convincing answer for
OL,16,Fthem."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1782251281
OL,3,CToddler suffered 'campaign of
OL,4,Cviolence' before death, jury hears
OL,6,FMr Wright said the couple had an
OL,7,F"unhealthy" relationship in which
OL,8,Fdrink and drugs were a feature, and it
OL,9,Fled to the decline in Isabelle's care
OL,10,Fbefore it built to her being
OL,11,F"subjected to regular violence at home
OL,12,Fby these defendants".
OL,14,FHe said, unusually, there was CCTV
OL,15,Fcaptured from two cameras installed at
OL,16,FWalker's home.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
