OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1782251281
OL,3,CToddler suffered 'campaign of
OL,4,Cviolence' before death, jury hears
OL,6,FMr Wright read an early message from
OL,7,FWalker to her new boyfriend in which
OL,8,Fshe said she was the primary carer for
OL,9,Fher daughter and was in the final year
OL,10,Fof studying forensics.
OL,12,FWalker and Simpson deny all charges
OL,13,Fand the trial at Teesside Crown Court
OL,14,Fcontinues.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G11/11
